        1.1 (2025-07-11)
        ----------------
        
        - Fixed installation by renaming the `base` profile to `install-base` so it is
          no more alphabetically before `default`.
          Removed `metadata.xml` from the `install-base` profile.
          [gbastien, aduchene]
        
